### React Components Using Hypothetical useOnlineStatus Hook

Source: https://github.com/reactjs/react.dev/blob/main/src/content/learn/reusing-logic-with-custom-hooks.md

Demonstrates how two React components, `StatusBar` and `SaveButton`, would look if a `useOnlineStatus` hook were available. This highlights the duplicated online status logic that can be abstracted into a custom hook.

```js
function StatusBar() {
  const isOnline = useOnlineStatus();
  return <h1>{isOnline ? '‚úÖ Online' : '‚ùå Disconnected'}</h1>;
