### Incorrect useFormStatus Usage: Hook in Same Component as Form

Source: https://github.com/reactjs/react.dev/blob/main/src/content/reference/react-dom/hooks/useFormStatus.md

Illustrates an incorrect usage pattern where `useFormStatus` is called in the same component that renders the `<form>`. This will prevent the `pending` state from updating correctly, as the hook only tracks parent forms.

```javascript
function Form() {
  // üö© `pending` will never be true
  // useFormStatus does not track the form rendered in this component
  const { pending } = useFormStatus();
  return <form action={submit}></form>;
}
```

