### React `ChatRoom` Component Passing `onReceiveMessage` Prop

Source: https://github.com/reactjs/react.dev/blob/main/src/content/learn/reusing-logic-with-custom-hooks.md

This React component demonstrates how to pass a custom `onReceiveMessage` event handler as a prop to the `useChatRoom` hook. This approach allows the component to define what action to take when a new message is received from the chat, making the hook more flexible.

