   512‚Üí
   513‚Üí## Reference Documentation
   514‚Üí
   515‚ÜíFor comprehensive details on React best practices, patterns, and anti-patterns, refer to:
   516‚Üí- `references/react_best_practices.md` - Complete guide covering hooks, component patterns, purity, immutability, custom hooks, and modern React features
