   525‚Üí## Implementation Checklist
   526‚Üí
   527‚ÜíWhen creating or reviewing React components, verify:
   528‚Üí
   529‚Üí- [ ] Component defined at module level (not inside another component)
   530‚Üí- [ ] All hooks called at top level (no conditionals, loops, or early returns before hooks)
   531‚Üí- [ ] Hooks called in consistent order every render
   532‚Üí- [ ] State never mutated directly (always use setState with new values)
   533‚Üí- [ ] Props never mutated
   534‚Üí- [ ] No mutations after values passed to JSX
   535‚Üí- [ ] useEffect includes all dependencies
