   539‚Üí- [ ] Derived state calculated during render (not in useEffect)
   540‚Üí- [ ] Custom hooks prefixed with "use"
   541‚Üí- [ ] Custom hooks follow Rules of Hooks
   542‚Üí- [ ] No hooks passed as props
   543‚Üí- [ ] Component is pure (same props ‚Üí same output)
   544‚Üí- [ ] Performance optimizations only applied after measuring
   545‚Üí
   546‚Üí## Common Debugging Steps
   547‚Üí
   548‚ÜíWhen encountering React issues:
   549‚Üí
   550‚Üí1. **State not updating**: Check for direct mutations, verify setState is called with new values
   551‚Üí2. **Infinite re-renders**: Check useEffect dependencies, verify state updates aren't unconditional
   552‚Üí3. **Stale closures**: Ensure dependencies are complete in useCallback/useMemo/useEffect
   553‚Üí4. **Hook errors**: Verify hooks are at top level, not conditional
   554‚Üí5. **Component not re-rendering**: Check if props/state are actually changing (reference equality)
